keyFacts: Document is a witness coordination schedule showing planned depositions or interviews from late November to mid-December 2006.
Includes logistical notes about keeping certain witnesses at different hotels, suggesting coordination to prevent witness interaction.
Lists various records custodians (birth certificate, AT&T, PB School District, FedEx) indicating document requests for the case.
Includes law enforcement witnesses from Palm Beach Police Department and FBI agents from New York.
Shows witnesses from multiple states including Florida, California, New York, Arizona, Rhode Island, Michigan, Texas, and Arkansas.
